npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Session work products — screenshots, audit notes, scratch dirs. Kept
# locally for in-progress reference, never shipped to production.
.audit/
.audit-shots/
.tmp-screens/
audits/
consistency-audit.md